'''Anne''' is one of the lawyers who represented the hospital in the plane crash lawsuit.

==History==
Anne and [[Michael Baker]] questioned Owen about the details surrounding the plane crash. They informed him that he had signed off on making the change between their previous charter company and the new one, which had a history of mechanical failures.

==Career==
Anne is a lawyer. She and Michael Baker represented the hospital in the plane crash lawsuit.
